After nine month break, I started four weeks practice to prepare Meta phone screen. I choose to work on sliding window algorithms. 
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. Binary search to find the position in the list to insert
2. Sliding window - size is k, removal - find the element using O(k) time, insert, using O(logk) time - using BinarySearch find the position to insert
3. Benefits of BinarySearch - no worry about index-out-of-range, index position is calculated, use bitwise operator ~
