which means there are two members with same color.
Even though arr[2] is '1', it doesn't meant that it is same color as arr[0], arr[1] because arr[0] tells that there is one member who is same as itself(i.e arr[1]). So the arr[2] is considered to be a new color which tells there is one more member as itself.
For every i, the maximum no.of.rabbit with same color is i + 1.
